'''B堆'''（{{lang-en|B-heap}}）是一个用来保证子树在一个内存页的[[二叉堆|二叉堆]]。这样可以在使用[[虚拟内存|虚拟内存]]时减少访问很大堆时内存页的访问。传统的实现中，元素位置的映射（几乎）每一级都放在不同的内存页中。

也有其他非常高效实用虚拟内存和缓存的堆的变种，例如{{le|缓存忽略算法|cache-oblivious algorithms}}、k堆、<ref>{{Cite journal|last1 = Naor|first1 = Dalit|last2 = Martel|first2 = Charles U.|last3 = Matloff|first3 = Norman S.|title = Performance of Priority Queue Structures in a Virtual Memory Environment|doi = 10.1093/comjnl/34.5.428|journal = [[The_Computer_Journal|Comput. J.]]|volume = 34|issue = 5|pages = 428–437|year = 1991|pmid = |pmc = }}</ref>和{{le|van Emde Boas树|Van Emde Boas tree}}。<ref>{{Cite journal|last1 = van Emde Boas|first1 = P.|last2 = Kaas|first2 = R.|last3 = Zijlstra|first3 = E.|title = Design and implementation of an efficient priority queue|doi = 10.1007/BF01683268|journal = [[Theory_of_Computing_Systems|Mathematical Systems Theory]] <!-- current name|name 1967–1996 -->|volume = 10|pages = 99–127|year = 1976|pmid = |pmc = |url = http://www.springerlink.com/content/h63507n460256241/}}{{Dead link}}</ref>

